 Docker, or required environment setup.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Avoid basing core tests on YAML, JSON, TOML, HOCON, AWS, Azure, Consul, Vault, HDFS, or watcher features unless the corresponding Hoplite module is intentionally added by the workflow; hoplite-core itself supports MapPropertySource and Java .props/.properties parsing out of the box. If testing SystemPropertiesPropertySource or EnvironmentVariablesPropertySource, set and clear test-local properties/variables within the test to avoid relying on ambient CI state.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The README's common examples use YAML and note that non-properties formats require separate hoplite-* format modules; generated tests that copy those examples verbatim would fail without adding hoplite-yaml, but that is not necessary for meaningful hoplite-core coverage.\",\n    \"The 3.0.0.RC1 artifact moves Kotlin transitive dependencies to 2.1.0, so failures may relate to Kotlin/GraalVM metadata rather than missing external setup.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06f2acb182939b9a016a43000b81308197a8bc3a5b60933e5a\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 284, "output": 800, "cacheRead": 24576, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 25660, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782775809669, "responseId": "resp_06f2acb182939b9a016a4300023e5c8197b700a9dc5943e664"}}
